  "Michael McCain is the CEO of Maple Leaf Foods, a Canadian packaged meat company that made $3.1 billion in sales in 2019.",
  "McCain's father, Wallace McCain, cofounded frozen food company McCain Foods with his brother Harrison in 1956.",
  "The family bought a controlling stake in Maple Leaf Foods in 1995.",
  "In January 2020, Michael McCain grabbed headlines for his scathing tweets about then-U.S. President Donald Trump and his foreign policy."
